<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7a87b87c-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s8519"><num value="8519">§ 8519.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="id7a87b87d-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s8519/a"><num value="a" class="bold">(a)</num><heading class="bold"> In general</heading><chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated to the Office of Oceanic and Atmospheric Research to carry out this subchapter—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id7a87b87e-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s8519/a/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><chapeau> $136,516,000 for fiscal year 2019, of which—</chapeau><subparagraph style="-uslm-lc:I13" class="indent2" id="id7a87b87f-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s8519/a/1/A"><num value="A">(A)</num><content> $85,758,000 is authorized for weather laboratories and cooperative institutes;</content>
