</subparagraph>
<subparagraph style="-uslm-lc:I13" class="indent2" id="id7a87b888-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s8519/a/3/B"><num value="B">(B)</num><content> $41,396,000 is authorized for weather and air chemistry research programs; and</content>
</subparagraph>
