</subparagraph>
<subparagraph style="-uslm-lc:I13" class="indent2" id="id7a87b88c-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s8519/a/4/B"><num value="B">(B)</num><content> $41,896,000 is authorized for weather and air chemistry research programs; and</content>
