<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id7a87b88e-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s8519/a/5"><num value="5">(5)</num><chapeau> $154,154,000 for fiscal year 2023, of which—</chapeau><subparagraph style="-uslm-lc:I13" class="indent2" id="id7a87b88f-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s8519/a/5/A"><num value="A">(A)</num><content> $91,758,000 is authorized for weather laboratories and cooperative institutes;</content>
