<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="id7a87b892-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s8519/b"><num value="b" class="bold">(b)</num><heading class="bold"> Limitation</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">No additional funds are authorized to carry out this subchapter and the amendments made by this title.<ref class="footnoteRef" idref="fn002600">1</ref><note type="footnote" id="fn002600"><num>1</num> See References in Text note below.</note></p>
</content>
</subsection>
